Class
Description
Board
A Board instance represents a board configuration for a game of PicturePuzzle.
Cell
Represents a single "cell" in the game showing part of the image.
Game
A Game instance represents a running game of PicturePuzzle.
GamePanel
GamePanel defines a panel to show the game.
Location
An location represents the position of a cell on a board.
Move
Responsible for moving a cell from a given position on the board into the "blank" cell.
